---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Home Backup Power Buying Guides (2026)" description="Buying guides for portable power stations, whole-home generators, solar generators, and battery backup. Practical picks for keeping your home running when the grid goes down.">

  <section class="bg-gray-50 border-b border-gray-100">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 py-16">
      <p class="text-xs font-semibold text-green-700 uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">Category Guide</p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Home Backup Power</h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 max-w-2xl leading-relaxed">
        Buying guides for portable power stations, whole-home generators, and solar setups.
        Practical picks for keeping critical systems running when the grid goes down.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 py-16">

    <!-- Portable Power Stations -->
    <section class="mb-16">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-2">
        <span class="text-2xl">🔋</span>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">Portable Power Stations</h2>
      </div>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-6 ml-10">Battery-powered backup for outages, camping, and remote work — no gasoline, no fumes, safe to use indoors.</p>
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
        <a href="/backup-power/best-portable-power-station-under-500" class="group block border border-gray-100 rounded-xl p-5 hover:border-green-200 hover:shadow-sm transition-all">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-1 group-hover:text-green-700 transition-colors text-sm">Best Portable Power Stations Under $500 →</h3>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">5 models at the sub-$500 sweet spot. EcoFlow DELTA 2 leads for most homeowners — 1024Wh and LFP battery at this price is hard to beat.</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/backup-power/best-portable-power-station-under-1000" class="group block border border-gray-100 rounded-xl p-5 hover:border-green-200 hover:shadow-sm transition-all">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-1 group-hover:text-green-700 transition-colors text-sm">Best Portable Power Stations Under $1,000 →</h3>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">4 picks from the $500–$1,000 tier — larger capacity, faster charging, and expandable options for serious home backup.</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/backup-power/best-backup-power-home-office" class="group block border border-gray-100 rounded-xl p-5 hover:border-green-200 hover:shadow-sm transition-all">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-1 group-hover:text-green-700 transition-colors text-sm">Best Backup Power for Home Office →</h3>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">Clean sine wave output and EPS mode for seamless switchover. Keep your laptop, monitor, and router running through any outage.</p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Whole-Home Generators -->
    <section class="mb-16">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-2">
        <span class="text-2xl">⚡</span>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">Whole-Home Standby Generators</h2>
      </div>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-6 ml-10">Permanently installed generators that start automatically within seconds of a power outage — no action required.</p>
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
        <a href="/backup-power/best-whole-home-generator-2000-sq-ft" class="group block border border-gray-100 rounded-xl p-5 hover:border-green-200 hover:shadow-sm transition-all">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-1 group-hover:text-green-700 transition-colors text-sm">Best Whole-Home Generator for 2,000 Sq Ft →</h3>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">Generac vs Kohler vs Briggs & Stratton. Covers sizing, natural gas vs propane, and total installed cost.</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/backup-power/best-whole-home-generator-for-well-pump" class="group block border border-gray-100 rounded-xl p-5 hover:border-green-200 hover:shadow-sm transition-all">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-1 group-hover:text-green-700 transition-colors text-sm">Best Whole-Home Generator for Well Pumps →</h3>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">Well pumps have high startup surge demands. The right generator size depends on pump horsepower — we break it down.</p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Solar Generators -->
    <section class="mb-16">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-2">
        <span class="text-2xl">☀️</span>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">Solar Generators</h2>
      </div>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-6 ml-10">Pair solar panels with battery storage for extended backup that recharges itself — no grid required.</p>
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
        <a href="/backup-power/best-solar-generator-home-backup" class="group block border border-gray-100 rounded-xl p-5 hover:border-green-200 hover:shadow-sm transition-all">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-1 group-hover:text-green-700 transition-colors text-sm">Best Solar Generators for Home Backup →</h3>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">EcoFlow's solar lineup compared — from the portable River 2 Pro to the high-capacity DELTA 2 Max. Full recharge times included.</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/backup-power/ecoflow-vs-jackery" class="group block border border-gray-100 rounded-xl p-5 hover:border-green-200 hover:shadow-sm transition-all">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-1 group-hover:text-green-700 transition-colors text-sm">EcoFlow vs Jackery: Full Comparison →</h3>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">The two most popular portable power brands side by side. Which wins on value, battery chemistry, and long-term reliability?</p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Specialty Backup -->
    <section class="mb-4">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-2">
        <span class="text-2xl">🏠</span>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">Specialty Backup</h2>
      </div>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-6 ml-10">Targeted backup solutions for specific needs — basement flooding, HVAC, and critical appliances.</p>
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
        <a href="/backup-power/best-battery-backup-sump-pump" class="group block border border-gray-100 rounded-xl p-5 hover:border-green-200 hover:shadow-sm transition-all">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-1 group-hover:text-green-700 transition-colors text-sm">Best Battery Backup for Sump Pumps →</h3>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">Dedicated sump backup units vs portable power stations. Which approach protects your basement better during storms?</p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>

  </div>
</Layout>
